5 A BILL
6 TO BE ENTITLED
7 AN ACT
8
9 To make supplemental appropriations from the Rural
10 Health Transformation Program to the Alabama Department of
11 Economic and Community Affairs for the fiscal year ending
12 September 30, 2026; and to create the Joint Legislative
13 Oversight Committee on Rural Health Transformation Program
14 Funds.
15 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF ALABAMA:
16 Section 1. In addition to all other appropriations
17 heretofore or hereafter made, there is hereby appropriated a
18 total of up to $203,404,327 in federal funds from the One Big
19 Beautiful Bill Act of 2025 (P.L. 119-21) for the Rural Health
20 Transformation Program to the Alabama Department of Economic
21 and Community Affairs ("ADECA") for the fiscal year ending
22 September 30, 2026 for the following:
23 (1) To the Collaborative EHR, IT, and Cybersecurity
24 Initiative, up to $31,425,971.
25 (2) To the Rural Health Initiative, up to $55,936,190.
26 (3) To the Maternal and Fetal Health Initiative, up to
27 $6,102,130.
28 (4) To the Rural Workforce Initiative, up to
